                <note rend="inline" type="source">868.01/8–1944</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of Conversation, by the Assistant Chief of the
                        Division of Near Eastern Affairs</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Kohler</hi>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-19">August 19,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Greek Ambassador told me this morning that he had received an official
                    telegram from his Government announcing that EAM was joining the Government
                    without any condition whatsoever and that its representatives were en route to
                    take up their Cabinet positions.</p>
            </div>
